        "how_to_trigger": "1. Enter \"spawnItem UNI_S_DebugBook_31ee023c-d151-40f6-917e-84066772783b\" into ReCon to spawn the DebugBook2. Use the DebugBook to travel to ACT1: Crash Site3. Enter \"goto -452.25, 13.51, -381.75\" into ReCon to travel into the Blighted Village smithy4. Activate the Melting Furnace5. Activate the Blacksmith's Bellows6. Enter \"create QUEST_FOR_SussurBark\" into ReCon to spawn the Sussur Tree Bark7 Enter \"create WPN_Dagger\" into ReCon to spawn a dagger in your inventory8. Use the Melting Furnace to combine the Sussur Bark with the Melting Furnace9. Exit and re-enter the Melting Furnace crafting menu10. Add the 'Dagger' to the crafting menu"
